{"tid":619902,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"咳左成個月有多","createTime":"2018-04-07T06:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T00:00:57.000Z","uid":63188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"30f779e8f4c4b516aa22cdb22e04021d137dad2a","tid":619902,"uid":63188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:12:20.000Z","msg":"咳左成個月，係冇啖個隻咳，好痕個種，咳得好密，去睇醫生，佢是但攞支電筒照下，之後就開咳水比我，飲完係好咗少少， 但真係得少少，<br />\n用晒之後都係咁咳，一直無好過<br />\n到底係咩原因，會唔會係啲氣管敏感呢<br />\n<br />\n有冇連登華佗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2994843e5f24acde205c858795d2b68578f27214","tid":619902,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"之前有fd都係咁 下世小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8a0469b5a60ec9960ecbf8748842478e0aca81","tid":619902,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:20:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"98f4740f7a48546346e3122568f93395936cf15c","tid":619902,"uid":8986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:32:51.000Z","msg":"紅糖煲薑 <br />\n要好熱個時飲 熱到乸喉個隻<br />\n戒菜戒水果一排 直到好返曬先食返"},{"pid":"7cd6cf50858b19a2de73f1b25db9a5569804ed44","tid":619902,"uid":3093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:38:17.000Z","msg":"我三個星期前都開始係咁<br />\n一吸大啖啲氣喉嚨就勁痕即刻狂咳<br />\n呢兩日食下枇杷膏同飲黑糖薑茶好似好左"},{"pid":"3e2c6637fcb5050e5bb1ca1604a7595305dbedd7","tid":619902,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"咳左兩個幾月，睇左好多次醫生，結果診斷出似鼻敏感，一食抗敏藥、噴鼻同洗鼻即刻無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c796782079f32caac2d78bbdcff2b6e3f4d5ec57","tid":619902,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43647ff510b935d9275f59a0346521b794120ee6","tid":619902,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:40