我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咳到而家都訓唔到然後見到呢個post <br />\n睇左醫生照過肺又話無事，而家咳到失聲喉嚨痛都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d6d58f645e414dff287c0b5c3de49cf15b20d4","tid":619902,"uid":146654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T00:00:57.000Z","msg":"細個個陣咳咗三個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n醫生話係氣管敏感 最嚴重個陣吸過類似擴張氣管嘅嘢 個陣係隻小學雞 唔太肯定係咩<br />\n之後好返係靠飲菜湯 同狂食supplement<br />\n而家一轉天氣都會咳一兩星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}